    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《沙盒与副本：英勇之地》品牌升级，正式更名为《英勇之地》！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个危机四伏的大陆中，四处充斥着强大的怪物以及敌人。玩家野蛮生长、弱肉强食，顶着死亡清零的风险，不断地冲击更强的武器和装备。跳动的实时排行榜下，强者在成神的路上，但其他人也在弑神的路上，你究竟该如何生存下去？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/a4cdc5f2314bc16008dc6f113c30b5f6.poster.avif?t=1770341966\" width=618 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/a4cdc5f2314bc16008dc6f113c30b5f6.webm?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/a4cdc5f2314bc16008dc6f113c30b5f6.mp4?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险之旅在初次走出安全区后即刻展开：没有繁琐的日常和任务，只有刷不完的资源和怪物，以及并存的无限危机。取出仓库和背包的藏品，和出售战利品升级，都能保证你能迅速投入到一把又一把刺激的战斗之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/686b152c3ef7b7d340a867c14f20c45c.poster.avif?t=1770341966\" width=618 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/686b152c3ef7b7d340a867c14f20c45c.webm?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/686b152c3ef7b7d340a867c14f20c45c.mp4?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有击败各色强大的怪物爆出稀有的武器和装备，才能获得抗衡其他玩家的绝对实力。玩家可以操作技能各异的英雄迅速发育，快速投入到挑战地图霸主的冒险之中。不停地战斗变强就是最佳的生存方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/94a31f56f19a786724fb705585e34609.poster.avif?t=1770341966\" width=618 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/94a31f56f19a786724fb705585e34609.webm?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/94a31f56f19a786724fb705585e34609.mp4?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦死亡将会失去大量的等级和积分，在危险的地图里，死亡还会掉落装备和武器。致命的险要之地往往奖励惊人，每局活得越久又往往能获得越多的奖励。在局内赌上一切猎取顶级装备资源，在局外解锁英雄、宠物和天赋，下一把的你一定是更强大的你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/99f9a4df891d8ce936580f30ee03bc9a.poster.avif?t=1770341966\" width=618 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/99f9a4df891d8ce936580f30ee03bc9a.webm?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/99f9a4df891d8ce936580f30ee03bc9a.mp4?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏上线了双排吃鸡战场、大逃杀、公会战等丰富的PVP活动，玩家可以根据战局随意搭配和切换多样的武器和装备，同时活用弹板、箭塔、兽夹等多款建造物，在战场上打出灵活的爆炸伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/62657224494a6755afe970705e5b3eb6.poster.avif?t=1770341966\" width=618 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/62657224494a6755afe970705e5b3eb6.webm?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349820/extras/62657224494a6755afe970705e5b3eb6.mp4?t=1770341966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以组队挑战副本、守卫公主等各式趣味玩法，也可以和志同道合的好友一起组建工会开荒称霸。还能携带最多3个技能各异的宠物，成为你在冒险中安身立命的超强战力。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "简体中文, 英语, 繁体中文, 日语, 韩语, 泰语, 越南语, 印度尼西亚语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙",
